            "content_number": "02",
            "heading": "Do you sell equipment for laundromats?",
            "row_content": "Yes. We work with laundromat owners on new laundromat projects, laundromat upgrades, retools, and equipment replacements. We can help with the planning process, equipment selection, layout support, installation coordination, and long-term support after the machines are in place."
